import { palette } from "./palette"

export const colors = {
  palette,
  transparent: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
  background: palette.white,

  primary: palette.orange,
  primaryDarker: palette.orangeDarker,

  line: palette.offWhite,
  text: palette.black,
  dim: palette.lightGrey,
  error: palette.angry,
}
